{"TopicId":186337,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Old Part Models as Cheap Career Mode Parts","CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T16:30:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T16:30:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m a sucker for nostalgia, and I\u0027d love to see the old part models (with smoothed textures) worked back into the game as cheaper and less efficient parts in career mode (but still made available in sandbox). Yes, this includes the old Mk1 Command Pod and the original spaceplane part models.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are a few ways this could be implemented...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. The parts are available by default as early tech pieces for some rudimentary launches.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. The parts are unlocked upon flying a large enough craft to KSC2 (my personal favorite idea since KSC2 keeps the original building designs).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. The parts become available as \u0022handouts\u0022 if the player goes over-budget, but the loan must be paid back later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd more, I\u0027m sure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T17:02:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook at this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002220067\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3461040953\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/89287-143-kerbal-historical-institute-presents-original-ksp-parts-37-040518/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T17:07:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m talking stock though.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T22:59:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMost likely will not happen. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-13T23:15:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223634483\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186337\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563058773\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMost likely will not happen. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*emotional deflation*\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;.;\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;.;\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}